Finally, we made it this far. Let's reclaim what is
important to us.
When you want to become stronger!

W-Well, I guess there's no helping it...!! B-Because I added

little bit, though!!

First, you can now do Party Formation! How about that,
surprised...!! You can freely form a party with your
favorite characters!

Talk to Tita in Lunaroa's Dream. I'm keeping it limited to
this location for now because I'm afraid of bugs. Be
careful, because if you return to the home base, the party
will be disbanded forcibly.

I don't know about things like balance and stuff anymore!
Each of you, play as you please!!

implement it...!!

Since there are no restrictions on party formation, if you
want to play, why not give it a try...? You don't have to
defeat it by force, so feel free to make use of it.

I think there might be some characters who can't participate
in the rematch or characters who speak even though they're
not participating... Well, don't worry about it!!

The final trial... It's where Lunaroa's Shadow was. I placed
the Great Boss there.
